Advisors,

Effective April 1, 2026, Flagstar Bank is updating IRA certificate rates across all tiers. The new rates are: Traditional IRA 12-month CD at 4.25% APY and Roth IRA 12-month CD at 4.15% APY. These are among the most competitive in the Michigan market.

Please use the updated rate sheets in the advisor portal for any client conversations starting Monday. This is a great opportunity to drive conversions on existing rollover prospects before the April 15 contribution deadline.

